  <description>
    <p>Find new AddOns and install them in a snap!</p>
    <p>Secure and easy AddOn management.</p>
    <p>NOTE: Snapshots of settings and addons don't work with Linux paths.</p>
    <p>NOTE: Hardware acceleration is disabled by default.</p>
    <p>NOTE: Minion may not list AddOns for the first time you use it, restarting it should fix the issue.</p>
